channel.description:
[center][img]http://ihaxx.net/logo.png[/img] Hey welcome to my thread for the development of iHaxx. My server started around the time i joined moparscape and since then i've wanted to create a successful server. But the only thing thats going wrong is my client, before i start anything i want to get my webclient up on my site. The next thing will be coding the server. I will need a bit of help with that :)
The source im going to be using is iRune Client + Server and start building off that. If you would like to help simply contact me on msn: Diesel@iHaxx.net or drop a reply
Pictures coming soon!
Website ~ www.iHaxx.Net Forums ~ N/A
Thanks For Reading, Elux[/center]
